264
00:14:04,690 --> 00:14:12,242
Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru!

265
00:14:12,330 --> 00:14:12,360
Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru!

266
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:17,620
