267
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:17,830
Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru!

268
00:14:17,830 --> 00:14:18,380
Ah, bahaya. Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru!

269
00:14:18,380 --> 00:14:19,120
Ah, bahaya.

270
