Tepat masanya.

284
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:50,830
Eh?

285
00:14:54,368 --> 00:14:56,992
Apa yang berlaku di sini?!

286
00:14:57,603 --> 00:15:00,760
Cicak, kalau kau mampu kalahkan dia,

287
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:02,640
