Wah, Ranga! Dia cukup tenang!

290
00:15:07,590 --> 00:15:10,500
Ya, tentulah. Kalau awak yang lawan, matilah dia.

291
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:12,190
Saya okey.

292
00:15:12,190 --> 00:15:15,052
Menghantar orang bawahan kau untuk bertarung supaya tak malu.

293
00:15:16,363 --> 00:15:18,331
Slime-dono setuju?

294
00:15:19,847 --> 00:15:22,200
Gobta, jangan berlembut! Ajar dia!

295
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,730
Kenapa saya yang perlu lawan?

296
00:15:24,730 --> 00:15:28,350
Kalau menang, saya akan minta Kurobe buat senjata khas awak awak!

297
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:31,110
Betul ni? Itu buat saya bersemangat!

298
00:15:31,110 --> 00:15:32,990
Kalau kalah, awak makan masakan Shion!

299
00:15:32,990 --> 00:15:34,747
Apa saja selain itu!

300
00:15:35,170 --> 00:15:38,573
Atas alasan tertentu, perbualan ini buat saya tak puas hati.

301
00:15:42,947 --> 00:15:45,260
Gabiru-sama!

302
00:15:45,260 --> 00:15:46,776
Dah sedia?

303
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:50,739
Baiklah, mulakan!

304
00:15:53,110 --> 00:15:54,460
Gabiru! Gabiru! Gabiru!

305
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:59,100
