309
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,782
Aku sendiri macam tak percaya!

310
00:16:29,070 --> 00:16:31,304
Gobta guna Gerakan Bayang-bayang?

311
00:16:38,230 --> 00:16:39,521
Itulah dia.

312
00:16:39,860 --> 00:16:42,390
Pertarungan tamat! Pemenangnya Gobta!

313
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:43,270
Bagus!

314
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:44,030
Syabas!

315
00:16:44,030 --> 00:16:45,119
Berjaya!

316
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:51,240
Bravo! Bravo!

317
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,472
- Tingginya! - Bravo! Bravo!

318
00:16:53,090 --> 00:16:56,993
Bagus, Gobta. Dari dulu lagi saya nampak potensi awak.

319
00:16:57,410 --> 00:17:01,585
Syabas kerana telah menunjukkan kemampuan sebenar Hobgoblin!

320
00:17:01,890 --> 00:17:03,370
Saya salah faham.

321
00:17:03,370 --> 00:17:08,290
Saya akan lupakan komen negatif awak sebelum ini.

322
00:17:08,690 --> 00:17:12,230
Sejak bertarung dengan kami, dia dah bertambah kuat.

323
00:17:12,230 --> 00:17:15,800
Nampaknya dia memiliki bakat yang perlu dipupuk.

324
00:17:16,830 --> 00:17:20,640
Adakah dia memang berbakat luar biasa?

325
00:17:21,060 --> 00:17:24,720
Selain itu, adakah semua orang fikir Gobta akan menang?

326
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:25,480
Ingatkan...

327
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:28,560
Kau akan menyesal...

328
00:17:28,560 --> 00:17:30,640
...kerana mencederakan orang kami!

329
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:33,210
Kau yang mula dulu, kan?

330
00:17:33,210 --> 00:17:36,860
...mereka cari gaduh dan orang itu teruk dibelasah.

331
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:42,870
Tak apa. Aku ni jenis orang yang tahu ikut rentak.

332
00:17:42,870 --> 00:17:44,780
Aku berpura-pura menjangkakan semua ini.

333
00:17:45,220 --> 00:17:46,540
Bagus, Gobta.

334
00:17:46,540 --> 00:17:49,160
Saya akan minta Kurobe buatkan awak senjata.

335
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,840
Hore!

336
00:17:50,990 --> 00:17:53,720
Kamu semua, Gobta dah menang!

337
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:59,960
Kami akan pertimbangkan kalau betul kamu perlukan bantuan kami untuk melawan Orc.

338
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,600
Tapi kami tak mahu di bawah kamu.

339
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:04,440
Bawa dia pergi dari sini.

340
00:18:06,150 --> 00:18:08,000
K-Kami akan kembali!

341
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:10,520
Ya. Ini belum berakhir!

342
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:12,650
Kami...

343
00:18:12,650 --> 00:18:15,760
Kami takkan lupa!

344
00:18:17,850 --> 00:18:19,280
Sekarang...

345
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:21,680
Rasanya kita perlu merancang tindakan seterusnya.

346
00:18:41,530 --> 00:18:43,370
Saya nampak 200,000 Orc.

347
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:47,060
Tentera utama bergerak ke utara di sepanjang sungai.

348
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:52,500
Berdasarkan pergerakan, rasanya mereka akan berkumpul

349
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:54,320
di kawasan paya sebelah timur.

350
00:18:54,770 --> 00:18:59,090
Itu wilayah Lizardmen, kan?

351
00:19:00,890 --> 00:19:02,306
200,000, ya?

352
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:05,601
Jumlah tu sangat besar, sukar dibayangkan.

353
00:19:10,130 --> 00:19:13,171
Orc nak apa sebenarnya?

354
00:19:15,660 --> 00:19:19,194
Orc bukan raksasa yang bijak.

355
00:19:19,930 --> 00:19:23,320
